Sentencas: The aim of this study was to develop La1-xBaxGa1-yMgyO3-delta (x = 0.03-0.1, y = 0.2-0.25) (LBGM) electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells (SOFCs); these electrolytes were synthesized via a solid-state reaction.
